  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Type 2 diabetes &gt; 1 year

          -  Age 18 years or older

          -  HbA1C &gt; 64 mmol/mol (8.0 %)

          -  Treatment with multiple daily insulin injections (basal and prandial insulin) ≥ 6
             months

          -  GAD-antibody negative

          -  Naïve to bolus calculators

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy or breast feeding

          -  Gastroparesis

          -  Severe nephropathy (eGFR&lt;30 mL/min/1,73 m2)

          -  Use of sulfonylurea
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
